
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-gu-l2vpn-vpls-bgp-signaling-00.txt'>
    <title>"Using BGP for Virtual Private LAN Service (VPLS) Signaling", Rui Gu, Jie Dong, Zhihua Liu</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-gu-l2vpn-vpls-bgp-signaling-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies a new BGP based signaling mechanism for providing Virtual Private LAN Service (VPLS) in large scale and multi-service networks.  This new mechanism combines the advantage of both the existing BGP based [RFC4761] and LDP based [RFC4762] VPLS mechanism.</description>
    <dc:date>2011-06-29T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
